text: Abu Dhabi (, ʼAbū Ẓaby) is one of the emirates that make up the United Arab Emirates. It is the largest of the seven. The capital city of UAE, Abu Dhabi, is in this emirate. Al Ain is Abu Dhabi's second largest urban area with a population of 766,936 (as of the 2017 estimate). Category:Current monarchies Category:Monarchies of Asia
title: Abu Dhabi (emirate)
